patthana14.33:4.1: Pariyāpannaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. #1
patthana14.33:5.1: Apariyāpannaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:5.2: Apariyāpannaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca napariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:5.3: Apariyāpannaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca napariyāpanno ca naapariyāpanno ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. #3
patthana14.33:6.1: Pariyāpannañca apariyāpannañca dhammaṃ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:7.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve … pe … avigate pañca.
